entry.title: THE OG BUNDLE
entry.summary:
Vendor: NAILZ BY DEV
Type: brush
Price: 33.00

Dev'z original nail art brush bundle. This set includes some of my top 3 favorite nail art brushes I create all my designs with! They are a must have for every nail artist!

BUNDLE INCLUDES:

💗Hella Cute Liner Brush- Perfect for Line work, character art, detailed designs. 15mm Nylon hair length. Wood Handle.

💗Lil' Baby Blender- Great for shading characters, blending small spaces, erasing mistakes, tie-dye, clouds, and more! Length: 4mm Width: 2mm 

💗AS IF! Ombre Brush- Made for creating gel polish ombre' designs! Length: 10mm Width: 8mm 

*How to use Ombre' brush:* (Apply first gel color, cure. Apply second color gel 1/3 of the way down nail, flush the ombre' brush level to the nail and lightly stroke down pulling the second color onto the first applied color. Use light tapping motions to blur any streaks! Cure.) *I suggest using this brush dry, not soaked in alcohol!*
